ANGULAR HELP COMMANDS
    ng g -h

CREATE component  (--skips-tests) to remove un nessary files paste it in src/app 
    ng g c nav --skip-tests

Angular template forms
#loginForm="ngForm"
CREATING angular Services
    ng g s account --skip-tests

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
connections of files and changes
in app component
app.component.ts -> app.component.html -> app.component.css -> app.module.ts -> app.routing.module.ts

in nav component
nav.component.ts ->app.component.html ->app.component.css -> account.service.ts
